  YLD101 [unsafe] Docstring yield type 'str' does not match type hint 'int'.
    --> yld101.py:11:9
     |
   9 | 
  10 |     Yields:
  11 |         str: Wrong type in docstring.
     |         ^^^
  12 |     """
  13 |     yield 42
     |
  
  ━━━ Diff ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  
  --- yld101.py
  +++ yld101.py (fixed)
  @@ -8,7 +8,7 @@
